024package org.opt4j.benchmarks.zdt;
025
026import static java.lang.Math.PI;
027import static java.lang.Math.exp;
028import static java.lang.Math.pow;
029import static java.lang.Math.sin;
030
031import org.opt4j.benchmarks.DoubleString;
032
033/**
034 * Function ZDT 6.
035 * 
036 * @author lukasiewycz
037 * 
038 */
039public class ZDT6 extends ZDT2 {
040
041        /*
042         * (non-Javadoc)
043         * 
044         * @see org.opt4j.benchmark.zdt.ZDT1#f1(org.opt4j.benchmark.DoubleString)
045         */
046        @Override
047        protected double f1(DoubleString x) {
048                double x0 = x.get(0);
049                double f1 = 1 - exp(-4 * x0) * pow(sin(6 * PI * x0), 6);
050                return f1;
051        }
052
053        /*
054         * (non-Javadoc)
055         * 
056         * @see org.opt4j.benchmark.zdt.ZDT1#g(org.opt4j.benchmark.DoubleString)
057         */
058        @Override
059        protected double g(DoubleString x) {
060                double sum = 0;
061                for (int i = 1; i < x.size(); i++) {
062                        sum += x.get(i);
063                }
064                double g = 1 + 9 * pow(sum / (x.size() - 1), 0.25);
065                return g;
066        }
067
068}
